<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ella Rises</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --pink: #FFD7D1;
            --blue: #A8C0CC;
            --text-gray: #4A4A4A;
            --purple-accent: #C4B7D3;
            --flower-red: #D9414E;
            --flower-lavender: #A7A9E0;
            --flower-yellow: #F4D57D;
            --flower-green: #799E82;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: white;
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Lato', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-gray);
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background-color: var(--pink);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(168, 192, 204, 0.3);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--pink), white);
            padding: 96px 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .hero-container {
            max-width: 56rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-container h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f2937;
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.25;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .hero-container h1 {
                font-size: 3.75rem;
            }
        }

        .hero-container p {
            margin-top: 24px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            max-width: 42rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .secondary-btn {
            background-color: white;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            border: 2px solid var(--text-gray);
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .secondary-btn:hover {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }

        .card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
     <%- include('navbar.ejs') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header>
        <div class="hero-container">
            <h1>Empowering Women to Rise</h1>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <button class="cta-btn">Get Involved</button>
                <button class="secondary-btn">Learn More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
